description: Police continue to investigate the shooting of a Greek Orthodox priest in the French city.
title: Lyon attack: Suspect in Orthodox priest shooting released
title_page: Lyon attack: Suspect in Orthodox priest shooting released - BBC News
maintext: In a statement on Saturday night, Lyon's public prosecutor, Nicolas Jacquet, said "a person who could correspond to the description given by the initial witnesses has been placed in police custody". He added that the suspect had not been carrying a weapon at the time of his arrest.
